.wrap-container-3
  .container
    .ar-app
      h2 
        span Our AR App
        .divider
      .text The use of AR, to provide a realistic representation of art in a 3D space, will help to drive more sales and will eliminate some of the problems associated with buying art online. It will also give the app real-world utility, making it much more than just a tool for passively browsing works of art
      ul.list.clearfix
        li.item
          .item__img
            img(src="images/app/photo1.png", data-rjs="images/app/photo1@2x.png", alt="")
        li.item
          .item__img
            img(src="images/app/photo2.png", data-rjs="images/app/photo2@2x.png", alt="")
        li.item
          .item__img
            img(src="images/app/photo3.png", data-rjs="images/app/photo3@2x.png", alt="")
    .pre-sale-token
      h2 
        span APT
        .divider
      .wrap-columns.clearfix
        .pre-sale-token__info
          ul.list
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Token name
              .col-2 APT
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Token type + designation
              .col-2 ERC20, utility
        .column-1
          ul.list
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Number of tokens minted
              .col-2 500,000,000
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Unsold tokens
              .col-2 Burned
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Public sale price
              .col-2 $0.15
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Pre-sale price
              .col-2 $0.1
        .column-2
          ul.list
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Accepted currencies
              .col-2 ETH
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Soft/Hard cap
              .col-2 $5m/$20m
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Team lockup
              .col-2 Six-month cliff, two-year vesting
            li.clearfix
              .col-1 Advisor lockup
              .col-2 Six-month cliff, six-month vesting
        
      .pre-sale-token__p The ArtPro token (APT) is an ERC20 usage token, divisible to six decimal places, which operates as a medium of exchange within the ArtPro network. 500 million tokens will be minted, 50% of which will be made available for public sale. Any unsold tokens will be burned.
      .pre-sale-token__p To fund development of the ArtPro platform and to create a diverse and distributed community, a token sale will be held in two phases, with a pre-sale starting in Q3 of 2018 followed by a public sale four weeks later.
      .pre-sale-token__p To participate in the ArtPro token sale, participants must complete whitelist registration.
